hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Do you play any instruments? runa clean energy drink review “I did the synopsis years ago,” he continues, “on a napkin in a café, one word for each chapter. I tore the strip off and put it in the back of a notebook because I knew I couldn’t write it. I wasn’t good enough, I wasn’t old enough, but the whole thing was there; I could see it. I’d drag it out once about every five years.” Eventually, his wife encouraged him “just to sit down and write it. I sat down in Caffè Nero and wrote the first chapter straight, without breaking. Then went home and kept writing.”
